'''热带风暴黛比'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Debby}}）是[[2006年大西洋飓风季|2006年大西洋飓风季]]形成的第5场[[热带气旋|热带风暴]]，源于8月21日[[非洲|非洲]]近海的一股[[东风波|东风波]]。从[[佛得角|佛得角群岛]]附近经过后，系统总体保持向西北方向移动，逐渐增强至[[最大持续风速|风速]]每小时85公里的最高强度。受强烈的[[风切变|风切变]]影响，风暴逐渐减弱，于8月27日在北[[大西洋|大西洋]]上空消散。

气象机构在黛比存在早期预测气旋会以热带风暴强度从佛得角群岛南部经过，并且有可能引发威胁生命的洪灾。多个计算机模型预计黛比会一直朝西北方向移动，但在强度预报方面遇到许多问题。美国国家飓风中心认为风暴会达到飓风标准，但受强烈风切变的影响，黛比的最高强度也没有超出热带风暴标准。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Debby 2006 track.png}}
8月20日晚，一股强劲的[[东风波|东风波]]离开[[非洲|非洲]]海岸，而且几乎立刻就发展出大范围环流和[[雨带|对流带]]<ref name="tcr">{{Cite web | author = James L. Franklin | date = 2006-11-02 | title = Tropical Storm Debby Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2012-11-02 | archivedate = 2012-11-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121102160153/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL052006_Debby.pdf | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL052006_Debby.pdf | format = [[PDF|PDF]] }}</ref>。次日，东风波行进至[[佛得角|佛得角群岛]]东南方向约420公里海域，其中已经有大规模[[低气压|低气压区]]形成。8月21日清晨，系统内的对流有所消退，但低气压区的组织结构仍然完整且层次分明<ref name="aug21two">{{cite report | author1 = Eric Blake | author2 = James Franklin | date = 2006-08-21 | title = August 21 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Cener}}</ref>，于当天晚上发展成[[2006年大西洋飓风季|2006年大西洋飓风季]]的第四号热带低气压。受北侧的[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响，低气压向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动，行经洋面[[海面温度|水温]]够高，上层风切变也很少。<ref name="td1disc">{{cite web | author = James L. Franklin | date = 2006-08-21 | title = Tropical Depression One Discussion One | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114201/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.001.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-31 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>由于多个模型都认定气旋会向西北方向移动，美国国家飓风中心起初也这样预测，但正如气象学家詹姆斯·富兰克林（{{lang|en|James Franklin}}）所说，这些模型也一直都在犯错误<ref name="tddisc1">{{cite web | author = James L. Franklin | year = 2006-08-22 | title = Tropical Depression Four Discussion Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-31 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.002.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114201/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.002.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。

低气压成形后不久，其中的[[对流|对流]]有所减退，但组织结构依然良好，规模也很庞大，风场直径有930公里<ref name="tddisc1" />。8月22日，气旋从佛得角群岛以南约225公里洋面经过，其环流中心上空已有深层对流发展出来<ref name="td4disc3">{{cite web | author = Daniel Brown | date = 2006-08-26 | title = Tropical Depression Four Discussion Three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-31 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114216/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.003.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.003.shtml? }}</ref>，美国国家飓风中心于8月23日清晨将位于佛得角西南方向约485公里海域的热带低气压升级成热带风暴，并以“黛比”（{{lang|en|Debby}}）命名<ref name="tcr" />。系统缓慢增强，[[雨带|带状特征]]继续组织<ref name="debbydisc7">{{cite web | author = Daniel Brown | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114230/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.007.shtml | date = 2006-08-23 | title = Tropical Storm Debby Discussion Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-31 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.007.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，黛比于8月23日在大西洋开放水域上空达到[[最大持续风速|风速]]每小时85公里的最高强度。气象机构预计气旋行经水域的水温比较高，上层风切变为中等强度，所以会继续增强至飓风标准。<ref name="debbydisc8">{{cite web | author = James L. Franklin | date = 2006-08-23 | title = Tropical Storm Debby Discussion Eight | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-31 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114231/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.008.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.008.shtml? }}</ref>

[[File:Tropical_Storm_Debby_TRMM_Image_(2006).jpg|right]]

达到最高强度后不久，黛比因遭遇干燥空气而减弱。系统整体仍在向西北偏西方向移动，但下层环流已经同逐渐消亡的对流分离<ref name="debbydisc9">{{cite web | author = James L. Franklin | date = 2006-08-23 | title = Tropical Storm Debby Discussion Nine | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-31 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114231/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.009.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.009.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。之后气旋中心上空部分区域有对流重新发展出来<ref name="debbydisc10">{{cite web | author = Stacy Stewart | date = 2006-08-24 | title = Tropical Storm Debby Discussion Ten | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114232/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.010.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.010.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>并持续组织，于8月24日再度达到风力时速85公里的最高强度<ref name="debbydisc12">{{cite web | author = James L. Franklin | date = 2006-08-24 | title = Tropical Storm Debby Discussion Twelve | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-31 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.012.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114249/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.012.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。南向风切变令对流偏移至中心北侧，8月25日时，黛比的强度已降至热带风暴的最低标准<ref name="debbydisc16">{{cite web | author1 = David Roberts | author2 = Jack Beven | date = 2006-08-25 | title = Tropical Storm Debby Discussion Sixteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-31 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114304/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.016.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.016.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。风暴中心变得细长且不对称<ref name="debbydisc18">{{cite web | author1 = Robbie Berg | author2 = Richard Knabb | date = 2006-08-26 | title = Tropical Storm Debby Discussion Eighteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2011-02-25 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.018.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114308/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.018.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>，于8月26日降级成热带低气压<ref name="debbydisc19">{{cite web | author1 = Eric Blake | author2 = Lixion Avila | year = 2006-08-26 | title = Tropical Depression Debby Discussion Nineteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2011-02-25 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.019.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114320/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.019.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。系统内未能重新发展出足够对流，很快就退化成残留低气压区。低气压区转向北上，之后又转朝东北偏北方向逐渐逼近的[[低压槽|低压槽]]前进，最终在8月28日完全消散。<ref name="tcr" />

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:TD_Four_21_aug_2006_1435Z.jpg|right]]
美国国家飓风中心针对第四号热带低气压发布首份公告的同时，佛得角群岛政府发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]，意指当地可能会在24小时内遭遇热带风暴袭击。美国国家飓风中心指出，该群岛可能会有暴雨，其中山区有可能高达250毫米，引发威胁生命安全的山洪和泥石流<ref name="td1pubadv">{{cite web | author = James Franklin | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114158/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.public.001.shtml | date = 2006-08-21 | title = Tropical Depression Public Advisory One | publisher = National Hurricane | accessdate = 2015-10-31 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.public.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。但由于气旋是在更偏南面的海域成形<ref name="tddisc1" />，热带风暴警告也随低气压的远离而中止<ref name="td4pubadv4">{{cite web | author = James Franklin | date = 2006-08-22 | title = Tropical Depression Four Public Advisory Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-31 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114211/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.public.004.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.public.004.shtml? }}</ref>。低气压在该群岛大部分岛屿西南方向约185公里洋面经过期间，[[福戈岛|福戈岛]]上的阵风时速达到55公里<ref name="tcr" />，还出现一定程度降水，但没有出现造成破坏的报道<ref name="capeverdeap">{{cite news |author=[[美联社|Associated Press]] |title=Tropical Depression Reaches Cape Verde Islands |accessdate=2015-10-31 |date=2006-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150127080732/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/08/22/tropical-depression-reaches-cape-verde-islands/?sPage=fnc.specialsections%2Fnaturaldisaster |archivedate=2015-01-27 |deadurl=yes |work=Fox News |url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/08/22/tropical-depression-reaches-cape-verde-islands?sPage=fnc.specialsections/naturaldisaster }}</ref>。

气象机构一直预报风暴会行进至[[百慕大|百慕大]]附近<ref name="capeverdeap" />，但黛比即便是在距该岛最近时也在超过1450公里外<ref name="debbydisc23">{{cite web | author1 = Eric Blake | author2 = Stacy Stewart | year = 2006 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114337/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.023.shtml | title = Tropical Depression Debby Discussion Twenty-three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-31 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al04/al042006.discus.023.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。气象部门还预计气旋会一直远离[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]，但投资者对风暴可能影响石油设施的担忧令每桶原油价格上涨了60美分<ref name="oil">{{cite news | newspaper = The Daily Star | date = 2006-08-26 | title = Oil prices higher in Asia | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150617060836/http://archive.thedailystar.net/2006/08/26/d60826051277.htm | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-10-31 | url = http://archive.thedailystar.net/2006/08/26/d60826051277.htm | archivedate = 2015-06-17 }}</ref>。

